Package: kivio
Architecture: any
Section: graphics
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: kdebase
Description: KDE Office Suite - Kivio
 KDE Office Suite - Kivio
 .
 Kivio on the surface is your everyday flowcharting program.  Underneath this
 skin, however, lies much more. Kivio will offer basic  flowcharting abilities,
 but with a twist. Objects are scriptable, and a backend plugin system will
 offer the ability to make objects do just about anything.

